.TH SOT "1" "2024\-2026" "sot" "Generated Python Manual"
.SH NAME
sot \- sot is a Command\-line System Observation Tool in the spirit of top. It displays various interesting system stats and graphs them. Works on all operating systems.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sot
[--help] [--version] [--log LOG] [--net NET] [--disk [DISK]] {info,bench,disk,clean,ps} ...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Command\-line System Observation Tool ≈

.SH
POSITIONAL ARGUMENTS
.TP
\fBsot\fR \fI\,info\/\fR
Display system information
.TP
\fBsot\fR \fI\,bench\/\fR
Disk benchmarking
.TP
\fBsot\fR \fI\,disk\/\fR
Interactive disk information viewer
.TP
\fBsot\fR \fI\,clean\/\fR
Deep clean system caches, logs, and temp files
.TP
\fBsot\fR \fI\,ps\/\fR
Interactive process viewer

.SH COMMAND \fI\,'sot info'\/\fR
usage: sot info [\-h]

.SH COMMAND \fI\,'sot bench'\/\fR
usage: sot bench [\-h] [\-\-output OUTPUT] [\-\-duration DURATION]

.SH OPTIONS \fI\,'sot bench'\/\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,OUTPUT\/\fR, \fB\-o\fR \fI\,OUTPUT\/\fR
Output file for benchmark results (JSON format)

.TP
\fB\-\-duration\fR \fI\,DURATION\/\fR, \fB\-d\fR \fI\,DURATION\/\fR
Duration for each benchmark test in seconds (default: 10s)

.SH COMMAND \fI\,'sot disk'\/\fR
usage: sot disk [\-h]

.SH COMMAND \fI\,'sot clean'\/\fR
usage: sot clean [\-h] [\-\-dry\-run]

.SH OPTIONS \fI\,'sot clean'\/\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be cleaned without actually deleting

.SH COMMAND \fI\,'sot ps'\/\fR
usage: sot ps [\-h]

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR, \fB\-V\fR
Display version information with styling

.TP
\fB\-\-log\fR \fI\,LOG\/\fR, \fB\-L\fR \fI\,LOG\/\fR
Debug log file path (enables debug logging)

.TP
\fB\-\-net\fR \fI\,NET\/\fR, \fB\-N\fR \fI\,NET\/\fR
Network interface to display (default: auto\-detect best interface)

.TP
\fB\-\-disk\fR \fI\,[DISK]\/\fR, \fB\-D\fR \fI\,[DISK]\/\fR
Disk mountpoint to display (use without value for interactive selection)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B sot
Launch the interactive system monitoring TUI
.TP
.B sot --net eth0
Monitor system with specific network interface
.TP
.B sot --disk
Interactive disk mountpoint selection
.TP
.B sot --disk /
Monitor system with root disk
.TP
.B sot info
Display comprehensive system information
.TP
.B sot bench
Run interactive disk benchmark
.TP
.B sot bench --duration 30 --output results.json
Run 30-second benchmarks and save results to JSON
.TP
.B sot disk
View interactive disk information
.TP
.B sot clean --dry-run
Preview what would be cleaned without deleting
.TP
.B sot clean
Deep clean system caches and temp files
.TP
.B sot ps
Launch interactive process viewer with ports and dev environments

